title: Dark Snake Premium v1.0.0
description:
This snake game contains:

- Nice design
- Original graphics and game system
- 40 stages
- Mazes
- Enemies

This PREMIUM version add the below features over free version:

- Integration with Google Play Games
* Automatically saving of the game progress
* Synchronized game progress over multiple devices with same account
* Achievements
- No adverts

All new features and bug fixes will come earlier to PREMIUM vesion
